column3: Status of the AI system (on the market, or in service; no longer placed on the market/inservice, recalled); - ANNEX VIII (6)
Status associated with the first making available of an AI system or a general purpose AI model on the market
Status associated with the first making available of an AI system or a general purpose AI model on the Union market

Status associated with supply of an AI system or a general purpose AI model for distribution or use on the market in the course of a commercial activity, whether in return for payment or free of charge

Status associated with supply of an AI system or a general purpose AI model for distribution or use on the Union market in the course of a commercial activity, whether in return for payment or free of charge

Status associated with supply of an AI system or a general purpose AI model for distribution or use on any market except the Union market in the course of a commercial activity, whether in return for payment or free of charge
not available on a market anywhere in EU or otherwise
Status asssociated with the supply of an AI system for first use directly to the deployer or for own use for its intended purpose
Status associated with an AI system that has not been put into service
Status asssociated with the supply of an AI system for first use directly to the deployer or for own use in the Union for its intended purpose
An AI System that is returned to the provider or taken out of service or use
An AI System that is prevented to be made available in the supply chain
